Sentencas: Characteristics of the porous Gd0.15Sr0.85CoO3-delta and La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-delta cathodes were compared using the data measured at different electrode potentials and oxygen partial pressures.
Titulo: Comparative study of the crystallographic expansion of GSC and LSC porous electrodes

Sentencas: The electrochemical high-temperature in situ XRD (HT-XRD) method combined with electrochemical impedance spectroscopy has been used.
Titulo: Comparative study of the crystallographic expansion of GSC and LSC porous electrodes

Sentencas: The response of the crystallographic parameters and impedance values on the changes of electrode potential has been discussed.
Titulo: Comparative study of the crystallographic expansion of GSC and LSC porous electrodes

Sentencas: Reversible changes of the lattice parameters for both cathodes, slower for Gd0.15Sr0.85CoO3-delta compared with La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-delta, were observed depending on temperature (T), electrode potential (E), and oxygen partial pressure (pO(2)).
Titulo: Comparative study of the crystallographic expansion of GSC and LSC porous electrodes

Sentencas: The crystallographic parameters are determined by the vacancy formation kinetics as well as by vacancy formation energy in/at the cathode grain structure.
Titulo: Comparative study of the crystallographic expansion of GSC and LSC porous electrodes

Sentencas: Calculated impedance data were fitted to the experimental data and characteristics were obtained in context of crystallographic changes of the cathode materials studied.
Titulo: Comparative study of the crystallographic expansion of GSC and LSC porous electrodes
